text:
Very friendly and courteous stall owners, food is priced reasonably and most importantly tastes so good! Must try for their chicken wings - crispy, succulent and nicely seasoned, nasi lemak was quite alright and bee hoon is a must try as well! not too salty - pair their wings with bee hoon and youâ€™re already set! Recommended for anyone looking for good juicy chicken wings for breakfast/lunch.

They open from mon - sat, 6am till 2.30pm!
Mee hoon must try. Very delicious.
The fried noodles are delicious. The fried eggs are delicious. The quality of the eggs is very good.
